
  <section id="base64-tool" class="section">
    <h2>Base64 Encode/Decode</h2>
    <p>Base64 is a method of converting text or files into 64 characters so that the data can be transmitted or stored safely.</p>
    <label for="base64-input"></label><textarea id="base64-input" rows="5" cols="50" placeholder="Enter your text here"></textarea>
    <br>
    <button id="encode-base64">Encode</button>
    <button id="decode-base64">Decode</button>
    <br>
    <label for="base64-output"></label><textarea id="base64-output" rows="5" cols="50" placeholder="Results are displayed here" readonly></textarea>
  </section>

